        {
            "title": "黃金和債券基金今年吸金規模勢創紀錄 資金亦強勢流入股票和現金基金",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 隨著不同類別資產之間傳統的相關性被打破，股票、現金、黃金和債券基金的年度資金流入規模有望位居歷史前列。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據美銀基於EPFR Global數據計算，從年迄今數據的年化表現來看，2025年股票基金有望吸引6930億美元的資金流入。該行策略師在報告中指出，這將創歷史第三高紀錄。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現金基金預計將吸引1.1萬億美元，創歷史第二高流入規模。投資者還在向黃金和投資級債券注入創紀錄資金，分別達1080億美元和4150億美元。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-fdf925ac-67a8-32a0-b966-5a6893b83e1a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kl7jBROPw0W3TvrzmDKsDg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5070513bd50a87c9357e6cf59efeea81\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國貿易政策的不可預測性是今年市場動盪的核心因素，考驗著投資者在各類資產間進行選擇的能力。圍繞聯儲會利率路徑的爭論，以及美國政府停擺導致的經濟數據真空，進一步加劇了局勢的複雜性。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管如此，隨著人工智能支出持續激增，加上企業盈利和經濟基本面保持穩健，股市仍創下歷史新高。隨著全球借貸成本下降，債券殖利率回落；黃金則因其在動盪時期作為避險資產的吸引力而飆升至歷史新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛集團宏觀交易員Bobby Molavi本周早些時候指出，債券、股票與黃金之間的歷史相關性已失靈，當前市場從許多方面來看可謂「後現代式」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Gold and Bonds Are Heading for Record-Breaking Inflows This Year</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Michael Msika.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%92%8C%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%B8%E9%87%91%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E5%8B%A2%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91%E4%BA%A6%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%A2%E6%B5%81%E5%85%A5%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E5%92%8C%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-120031068.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-25 10:10:45",
