            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美加對貿易談判進展各執一詞 卡尼稱等美國準備好後可恢復磋商\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fZecphR6TJPVXTgwVJqkDA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/f8189a30-b08b-11f0-957c-ba99d1c0a8cc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美加對貿易談判進展各執一詞 卡尼稱等美國準備好後可恢復磋商</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
